abstract: Britain's billionaire supermarket chain mogul David Sainsbury wins lively election to fill largely ceremonial chancellorship of Cambridge University.
snippet: In a lively contest to fill the largely ceremonial post of chancellor, Cambridge University graduates picked a billionaire businessman over three others, including a neighborhood grocer.
lead_paragraph: In a lively contest to fill the largely ceremonial post of chancellor, Cambridge University graduates picked a billionaire businessman over three others, including a neighborhood grocer.

headline.main: Cambridge Vote Ends With Supermarket Mogul on Top and Grocer in Last
headline.print_headline: Cambridge Vote Ends With Supermarket Mogul on Top and Grocer in Last
headline.seo: Cambridge Elects Supermarket Mogul as Chancellor
